{"tid":420372,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"現實冇人聽你講，唯有寫係日記簿上面","createTime":"2017-10-01T10:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T08:46:06.000Z","uid":12754,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"341e72b22bb1eb4e0b2afc90b2143ebe8cc61904","tid":420372,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:44:11.000Z","msg":"唔單只係經歷<br />\n寫寫下仲會流低幾滴眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0e59c7ddcc46cee2d1f707afe317eaff1f4bc7","tid":420372,"uid":141285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a69c2db128ef0ff812ceda5f2939a5a944278b","tid":420372,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"寫黎做乜"},{"pid":"5de88787a900f1c03b0db136b95b0f691310770d","tid":420372,"uid":145959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:39:15.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877825122578a7ac1f9e4742aacd29afd12935d1","tid":420372,"uid":128410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫黎做乜</blockquote><br />\n唔想自己忘記有過咁撚深刻/慘嘅經歷"},{"pid":"bf0b48b429175da60c4400bc05aa3a78c2c8b133","tid":420372,"uid":10371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"so true<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過係手機嘅notes"},{"pid":"6d90c0270d52efc63ff0b89028df6de18e1d0003","tid":420372,"uid":12754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>so true<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過係手機嘅notes</blockquote><br />\n手機始終有一日會壞會換<br />\n<br />\n同埋<br />\n搵個夜晚<br />\n飲住支啤酒<br />\n自己一個好靜咁寫字<br />\n一路寫一路喊<br />\n一路諗返自己點解咁撚柒咁撚on9<br />\n有個只係屬於自己既時間<br />\n可能都係冇現實生活入面唯一一支止痛劑"},{"pid":"88485814e62cb065509080be4e97257580bd50ef","tid":420372,"uid":71422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T15:57:39.000Z","msg":"我都會間唔中寫下 但只會用鉛筆 因為鉛筆有日會淡色咗<br />\n希望到時連我唔開心既事一齊退色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d1b2a491a2e585e9b52465126565594e3f9d90","tid":420372,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都會間唔中寫下 但只會用鉛筆 因為鉛筆有日會淡色咗<br />\n希望到時連我唔開心既事一齊退色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只係一個自欺欺人既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e2c9ede36b5cd179a4fbdc19bc3a9ece704b67","tid":420372,"uid":129145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T16:03:04.000Z","msg":"Yes 一有唔開心就寫低 有時喊到墨水都化開哂 <br />\n過一排就會睇返 會勾起好多就黎唔記得既細節 但同時會覺得原來果陣都冇咩咁大不了 仲捱得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c13987c6b1c2890dc4732bb7a828bbad31260c","tid":420372,"uid":135416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T18:38:30.000Z","msg":"傷春悲秋"},{"pid":"ac00e7f586cbd7e60932a13edbad8b6ba333b5e3","tid":420372,"uid":71422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:53:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都會間唔中寫下 但只會用鉛筆 因為鉛筆有日會淡色咗<br />\n希望到時連我唔開心既事一齊退色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只係一個自欺欺人既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但至少嗰一刻有人陪你分擔唔開心 講左出黎 舒服啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf54769c757f3fa14c951276a6534e1ed7aad870","tid":420372,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:58:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e87454a769a7f5f2ddfd690f1a77d79832186ca","tid":420372,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"寫日記都係一個舒發心情嘅好方法，寫出黎感覺好似會冇咁唔開心。但唔好收收埋埋，可以係依到呻下架！加油啊，樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}